OL,3,CNew fund to build thousands of homes,
OL,4,Ca college and sports facilities
OL,6,FJersey's government has revealed plans
OL,7,Fto set aside around #80 million a year
OL,8,Fto invest in capital infrastructure.
OL,10,FMinisters want to set up a dedicated
OL,11,Ffund, ringfencing money for planned
OL,12,Fprojects over the next 25 years.
OL,14,FThey include building thousands more
OL,15,Fhomes, a new college in the centre of
OL,16,FSt Helier, improved road and water
OL,17,Finfrastructure and upgraded sports
OL,18,Ffacilities.
