OL,6,FIf approved, the money would be
OL,7,Fsiphoned off from next year and given
OL,8,Flegal protection against being spent
OL,9,Felsewhere.
OL,11,FJersey's Chief Minister, Deputy Lyndon
OL,12,FFarnham, adds: "Sometimes ministers
OL,13,Fhave taken money from the capital
OL,14,Fexpenditure where it is not
OL,15,Fimmediately noticed. Doing that for
OL,16,Fyears has led to a situation where
OL,17,Fsome of our infrastructure is starting
OL,18,Fto show its age.
