OL,3,CNew fund to build thousands of homes,
OL,4,Ca college and sports facilities
OL,6,F"There's been no coordinated approach,
OL,7,Fthere's not been one consolidated plan
OL,8,Fthat looks right across the public
OL,9,Fsector to make sure we have a
OL,10,Fstructured, properly-funded capital
OL,11,Fplan.
OL,13,F"We also need to create a platform to
OL,14,Frebuild hope and confidence."
OL,16,FHighlands College would be refurbished
OL,17,Fand relocated under the plans, with an
OL,18,Faccessible, purpose-built campus for
OL,19,FFurther and Higher Education.
