OL,3,CNew fund to build thousands of homes,
OL,4,Ca college and sports facilities
OL,6,FPrincipal Jo Terry-Marchant says:
OL,7,F"It's really important for Jersey.
OL,8,FMore modern, fit-for-purpose
OL,9,Ffacilities will allow us to widen
OL,10,Faccess and opportunity to all age
OL,11,Fgroups.
OL,13,F"What is refreshing about this is that
OL,14,Fthey are looking at the interconnected
OL,15,Fnature of different priorities across
OL,16,Fthe island ... We have needed this for
OL,17,Fprobably more than a decade."
