OL,6,FPaul Wylie, Chief Officer of the
OL,7,FCabinet Office, adds: "We know
OL,8,FHighlands College campus needs
OL,9,Frenovating, so we're exploring putting
OL,10,Fit in the town centre.
OL,12,F"That brings young people into the
OL,13,Ftown centre and it frees up amazing
OL,14,Fsites at the top of the hill for
OL,15,Ffamily housing."
