OL,4,Ca college and sports facilities
OL,6,FHe explains: "Our partners in Andium
OL,7,FHomes and States of Jersey Development
OL,8,FCompany will be prioritising family-
OL,9,Fsize homes of three or four bedrooms,
OL,10,Fas opposed to flats as in the past."
OL,12,FHowever, backbench politicians are
OL,13,Falready questioning whether the
OL,14,FGovernment will have enough funds to
OL,15,Fpay for everything that is planned.
