OL,3,CNew fund to build thousands of homes,
OL,4,Ca college and sports facilities
OL,6,FDeputy Max Andrews says: "The money
OL,7,Fhas to come from somewhere ... I can
OL,8,Funderstand the reason behind the
OL,9,Fdecision to bring forward this new
OL,10,Ffund, but with the number of
OL,11,Fproperties the Government owns, we're
OL,12,Ftalking about hundreds of millions of
OL,13,Fpounds of investment.
OL,15,F"If we were spending our money more
OL,16,Fwisely, we wouldn't be in this
OL,17,Fposition in the first place."
OL,19,FBusiness leaders are also asking for
OL,20,Fmore clarity on the plans for
OL,21,Finvestment.
