OL,6,FJersey's Chamber of Commerce
OL,7,FPresident, Lee Madden, explains:
OL,8,F"Ambition must be matched by delivery.
OL,9,FOur members are asking the same
OL,10,Fquestions the public will be: how will
OL,11,Fthis be paid for, and will it be
OL,12,Fdelivered on time?"
