OL,6,FMeanwhile, Jersey's Hospitality
OL,7,FAssociation have thrown their support
OL,8,Fbehind the plan, stating: "This is a
OL,9,Flong-overdue step in recognising that
OL,10,Fsustainable economic growth,
OL,11,Fparticularly in the visitor economy,
OL,12,Fcannot happen without Government first
OL,13,Fdelivering the essential
OL,14,Finfrastructure that enables it.
OL,16,F"But words on a page are not delivery.
OL,17,FWhile we strongly support this
OL,18,Fdocument's content and its direction,
OL,19,Fthe success of this vision will depend
OL,20,Fentirely on competent, accountable
OL,21,Fleadership."
